name: Sku
description:
Encapsulates a single SKU in Google Cloud Platform

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.billing.v1.Sku

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: The resource name for the SKU. Example: "services/DA34-426B-A397/skus/AA95-CD31-42FE"

params.name: data.description
params.description: A human readable description of the SKU, has a maximum length of 256 characters.

params.name: data.category
params.description: The category hierarchy of this SKU, purely for organizational purpose.

params.name: data.service_regions
params.description: List of service regions this SKU is offered at. Example: "asia-east1" Service regions can be found at https://cloud.google.com/about/locations/

params.name: data.pricing_info
params.description: A timeline of pricing info for this SKU in chronological order.

params.name: data.service_provider_name
params.description: Identifies the service provider. This is 'Google' for first party services in Google Cloud Platform.
